Nitro, West Virginia

Nitro is a city in Kanawha and Putnam counties in the State of West Virginia, along the Kanawha River. The population was 7,178 at the 2010 census. Nitro is a part of the Huntington-Ashland, WV-KY-OH, Metropolitan Statistical Area (MSA).

Putnam County, West Virginia

Putnam County is a county located in the State of West Virginia. As of the 2010 census, the population was 55,486. Its county seat is Winfield.

St. Albans, West Virginia

St. Albans is a city in Kanawha County, West Virginia, United States, at the confluence of the Kanawha and Coal Rivers.
